#ident	"@(#)bkrs:bkintf.d/backups/bkrem/remove/Help	1.2.1.1"

ABSTRACT: Remove Entries from Backup Reminder Schedule
	The "remove" task allows you to remove entries from the backup
	reminder schedule.  Press the [CHOICES] key to display the current
	backup reminder schedule, then write down or remember the line
	numbers corresponding to the entries you want to remove.  Press
	[CANCEL] to return to the line number form, then enter the list of
	line numbers you want removed from the backup reminder schedule.
	You may separate line numbers by spaces or commas.  Press [SAVE]
	to remove the lines or, if you decide not to remove the lines,
	press [CANCEL] to leave the backup reminder schedule as it is.

TITLE: Remove Entries from Backup Reminder Schedule

F1:
	"Line Number(s): " Enter the list of line numbers to be removed.
